yTime":"2017-04-04T16:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>500 days of summer <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650c68efcd7f0f475a068f6e8a2a5a923820190b","tid":187021,"uid":85384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"高登3寶"},{"pid":"4e5a16e35aa90203f61795c7a4400c98338d234c","tid":187021,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"海神號遇險記<br />\n-人性，有無私、互助、鼓勵，有畏懼、羊群、退縮<br />\n-向命運低頭就輸<br />\n<br />\n魔法小奇兵<br />\n-有時要放低執著成見<br />\n-有時揸實一樣嘢可能比放開更傷<br />\n<br />\n怪形<br />\n-人互相猜疑比禽更恐怖更變幻無常<br />\n-講到尾：憑咩我要信你<br />\n<br />\n2001太空漫遊<br />\n-係進化定係被取代？係猿進做人定人取代猿，如果係後者HAL只係人類進化<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌得細力啲得唔得</span>"},{"pid":"404a2f9e3ae69794943e6027276e5c52df6c2aac","tid":187021,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:12:01.000Z","msg":"About time"},{"pid":"bf83f02d2ec03cbff99d99dd3d6df0317d8eb9f7","tid":187021,"uid":15558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T16:36:25.000Z","msg":"Lalaland last scene<br />\n<br />\n之後無幾耐就分左手。"},{"pid":"9ce2b3473f5aabd5ef7b835817269bac61490929","tid":187021,"uid":29651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"Cloud atlas 雲圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇完都好攰但真係好正 會令你不停問自己生命嘅意義 同埋片尾曲好好聽<br />\n<br />\nOur lives are not our own. From womb to tomb, we are bound to others, past and present, and by each crime and every kindness, we birth our future.<br />\n<br />\nMy life amounts to no more than one drop in a limitless ocean. Yet what is any ocean, but a multitude of drops?"},{"pid":"cdc38d37d9fffe115413646b02bb0854f69704cd","tid":187021,"uid":29651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小王子 不過準確黎講係書黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n細個睇唔明大個左先開始鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新果套戲我同啲friend喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784ddabdfc2e3130e8926677c2b4301a7110ec85","tid":187021,"uid":45799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:35:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45a7e557ab5c0225749791cc1ec18cc2aa1d3e6d","tid":187021,"uid":6896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"Pulp fiction <br />\n<br />\n記得中學係明珠睇<br />\n第一次覺得原來成套戲係度鳩up都可以咁好睇<br />\n之後就愛上QT d 戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c83f47f52f4227576b0522c6286da1bc6ffcb2","tid":187021,"uid":65893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"下妻物語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 太幸福會令人變廢柴"},{"pid":"0d99c6fca281abc374f5414543b2428c0d4d8db2","tid":187021,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"Manchester by the sea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d767aa3cd0958f03cd8ea3459429cad958ab21","tid":187021,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:37:38.000Z","msg":"fight club 標準答案<br />\n反社會主義<br />\n反物質主義"},{"pid":"b11741be4bbcac77cf0f62a3ce8fb12085d97e4e","tid":187021,"uid":35620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b2212511e3c931f8ac6f912707d19dd2b21f09","tid":187021,"uid":72433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"Watchmen<br />\n睇完會對社會人性好反感，所有嘢（姦殺兒童）都唔係上帝做成，係我地(人性)<br />\n反思咗人類存在其實唔重要，太渺小不值重視，我依家完全唔再關心所有嘢，例如環保／兒童被殺／貧窮，因為我地根本唔值得關心，人性本惡<br />\n另外乜嘢先係正義？殺幾百萬人換取幾十億人暫時嘅和平，定睇住核戰爆發一齊死？<br />\n<br />\nA live body and a dead body contain the same number of particles. Structurally, there's no discernible difference. Life and death are unquantifiable abstracts. Why should I be concerned?<br />\nOnce you realize what a joke everything is, being the Comedian is the only thing that makes sense. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04a4b27bf9c7c7a3280da94cefd67ed3ab6f2cb","tid":187021,"uid":90132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"LaLaLand<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己一個去睇 個時個前度咁啱有新女<br />\n然後我睇完LaLaLand睇見男女主角最後並無係埋一齊 心酸都喊住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c9d4109b35eb7f79b568634cd5ab811f3364a7","tid":187021,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:13:09.000Z","msg":"Awakenings<br />\n<br />\n無語問蒼天"},{"pid":"861120274491659ff408b39bda55b999eae7693f","tid":187021,"uid":83164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T19:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Watchmen<br />\n睇完會對社會人性好反感，所有嘢（姦殺兒童）都唔係上帝做成，係我地(人性)<br />\n反思咗人類存在其實唔重要，太渺小不值重視，我依家完全唔再關心所有嘢，例如環保／兒童被殺／貧窮，因為我地根本唔值得關心，人性本惡<br />\n另外乜嘢先係正義？殺幾百萬人換取幾十億人暫時嘅和平，定睇住核戰爆發一齊死？<br />\n<br />\nA live body and a dead body contain the same number of particles. Structurally, there's no discernible difference. Life and death are unquantifiable abstracts. Why should I be concerned?<br />\nOnce you realize what a joke everything is, being the Comedian is the only thing that makes sense. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwatchmen 我都有睇過 但巴打又諗得負面好多<br />\n我只會對性格差的人反感 依然好開心會有人仲無條件幫人       如果你問咩係正義 我都會想問 咩野係惡<br />\n大家都係為左自己唔同理由去生存 <br />\n例如我想保護屋企人 而殺左個壞人 <br />\n我只諗到 從來都無所謂善惡 正邪 <br />\n只不過係 <br />\n邊一個人佢的自私入面 包含住&quot;保護更多的人&quot; 就會被視為好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界就係不斷比較邊個人的自私所概括的範圍大。而去定義果個人 的&quot;善&quot; &quot;惡&quot; &quot;好&quot; &quot;壞&quot;"},{"pid":"78648b2a85b2fc3cb3e20535f02bdc59c3b75dde","tid":187021,"uid":58983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"斷背山，睇完之後我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aed2f3fa0d363681c206565186856ea5cb04ec3","tid":187021,"uid":53489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:15:23.000Z","msg":"東邪西毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f673d424efc3a46957b6654edab65d01bfe3353","tid":187021,"uid":72433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Watchmen<br />\n睇完會對社會人性好反感，所有嘢（姦殺兒童）都唔係上帝做成，係我地(人性)<br />\n反思咗人類存在其實唔重要，太渺小不值重視，我依家完全唔再關心所有嘢，例如環保／兒童被殺／貧窮，因為我地根本唔值得關心，人性本惡<br />\n另外乜嘢先係正義？殺幾百萬人換取幾十億人暫時嘅和平，定睇住核戰爆發一齊死？<br />\n<br />\nA live body and a dead body contain the same number of particles. Structurally, there's no discernible difference. Life and death are unquantifiable abstracts. Why should I be concerned?<br />\nOnce you realize what a joke everything is, being the Comedian is the only thing that makes sense. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nwatchmen 我都有睇過 但巴打又諗得負面好多<br />\n我只會對性格差的人反感 依然好開心會有人仲無條件幫人       如果你問咩係正義 我都會想問 咩野係惡<br />\n大家都係為左自己唔同理由去生存 <br />\n例如我想保護屋企人 而殺左個壞人 <br />\n我只諗到 從來都無所謂善惡 正邪 <br />\n只不過係 <br />\n邊一個人佢的自私入面 包含住&quot;保護更多的人&quot; 就會被視為好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界就係不斷比較邊個人的自私所概括的範圍大。而去定義果個人 的&quot;善&quot; &quot;惡&quot; &quot;好&quot; &quot;壞&quot;</blockquote><br />\n但係你一犧牲一小群無辜嘅人去救一大班無辜嘅人，個世界無論點都會定義你做「罪人」，即使你目的係救更多嘅人<br />\n其實我最贊同係Dr Manhattan句&quot;i can change almost anything but i can't change human nature&quot;，人性本身唔能夠改，你再睇番依家世界所有事，有邊幾樣有改變過？"},{"pid":"b082f734d865a8f7439ab36f193d0b9bfd6a335c","tid":187021,"uid":52238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:14:13.000Z","msg":"Into the wild <br />\n<br />\n睇完之後開始諗自己到底係到做緊咩野<br />\n人生真係想追求既係咩野"},{"pid":"66f31850afb6e7b8aa9ac42a4c7888bb2c3412a7","tid":187021,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斷背山，睇完之後我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完春光乍洩都有少少&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e78d1562b0186bbf0dce3645478c43549e6fed","tid":187021,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"Million Dollar Baby"},{"pid":"734f3b8056d2aabc5d1b3c0382ec4bb16831ca68","tid":187021,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>斷背山，睇完之後我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b47315b1d69b9d8b314afa0899a7f2bc1a07c1ac","tid":187021,"uid":22059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:53:25.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅 張柏芝 &lt;十二夜&gt;"},{"pid":"7b0d42443a899cc6b39bbd58c201d12ae188c519","tid":187021,"uid":2183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:56:21.000Z","msg":"In time<br />\n時間=金錢"},{"pid":"44a07fbf6a463006638bbce840d7aa3a0a3a0204","tid":187021,"uid":45459,"like":0,"dis