017-04-05T07:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Into the wild <br />\n<br />\n睇完之後開始諗自己到底係到做緊咩野<br />\n人生真係想追求既係咩野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSociety hope you no angry if i disagree"},{"pid":"529188cd38d8cf4ce862a19b827fc5c09291d0c1","tid":187021,"uid":83754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Watchmen<br />\n睇完會對社會人性好反感，所有嘢（姦殺兒童）都唔係上帝做成，係我地(人性)<br />\n反思咗人類存在其實唔重要，太渺小不值重視，我依家完全唔再關心所有嘢，例如環保／兒童被殺／貧窮，因為我地根本唔值得關心，人性本惡<br />\n另外乜嘢先係正義？殺幾百萬人換取幾十億人暫時嘅和平，定睇住核戰爆發一齊死？<br />\n<br />\nA live body and a dead body contain the same number of particles. Structurally, there's no discernible difference. Life and death are unquantifiable abstracts. Why should I be concerned?<br />\nOnce you realize what a joke everything is, being the Comedian is the only thing that makes sense. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你有冇諗過挖個隆埋左自己佢？"},{"pid":"947c75fa66132fd861259ca62d3bc1bd0811e5d0","tid":187021,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"有好多<br />\n最近既話有琴晚先番睇完既the fight club<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V985dmu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV985dmu.jpg&h=d013299d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/160807_c6ec6223714aaca3ee8f0f7022e5dc1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F160807_c6ec6223714aaca3ee8f0f7022e5dc1a.jpg&h=1243925b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T0AL3yf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0AL3yf.jpg&h=d2b4884f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f1e23394b0212a9bfbc613d0d879f2ac7f03f74","tid":187021,"uid":37157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>海底奇兵</blockquote><br />\n有咩體會</blockquote><br />\n部電話無喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6814c94cfae651a2c6a561c0ae3042409a8bf6b2","tid":187021,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"當這地球沒有貓救返我嘅人生<br />\n上年個時成個人因為屋企問題同self hatred成個人好down 冇動力做任何嘢 有自殘傾向<br />\n套戲講親情個段我睇兩次都喊 覺得套戲講得好中我 老母封信同老豆講多謝個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個時先醒起老豆老母好開心有我呢粒仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc3cee6ecc9144cca4e0474e202a14a7843f5fe","tid":187021,"uid":78988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Watchmen<br />\n睇完會對社會人性好反感，所有嘢（姦殺兒童）都唔係上帝做成，係我地(人性)<br />\n反思咗人類存在其實唔重要，太渺小不值重視，我依家完全唔再關心所有嘢，例如環保／兒童被殺／貧窮，因為我地根本唔值得關心，人性本惡<br />\n另外乜嘢先係正義？殺幾百萬人換取幾十億人暫時嘅和平，定睇住核戰爆發一齊死？<br />\n<br />\nA live body and a dead body contain the same number of particles. Structurally, there's no discernible difference. Life and death are unquantifiable abstracts. Why should I be concerned?<br />\nOnce you realize what a joke everything is, being the Comedian is the only thing that makes sense. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWatchmen 史上最underrated嘅電影 沒有之一<br />\nBtw 佢個Bob Dylan片頭都相當好j"},{"pid":"ad5eadb3c85840246ac62a07eb98608e2e51d9c8","tid":187021,"uid":39630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cloud atlas 雲圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇完都好攰但真係好正 會令你不停問自己生命嘅意義 同埋片尾曲好好聽<br />\n<br />\nOur lives are not our own. From womb to tomb, we are bound to others, past and present, and by each crime and every kindness, we birth our future.<br />\n<br />\nMy life amounts to no more than one drop in a limitless ocean. Yet what is any ocean, but a multitude of drops?</blockquote><br />\n呢段對白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人話好長 但我睇個時就唔覺<br />\n咁多個故事佢都講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f494d8db703afc6050ada619444357fbe74ce56","tid":187021,"uid":78988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T08:54:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pulp fiction <br />\n<br />\n記得中學係明珠睇<br />\n第一次覺得原來成套戲係度鳩up都可以咁好睇<br />\n之後就愛上QT d 戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鳩up得嚟都好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實佢呢個兜亂晒嘅時間線入面 每個角色鳩吓鳩吓做嘅每一樣嘢都好似蝴蝶效應咁影響緊每一個人 最後兜番轉頭影響自己<br />\n同埋其實世界好細 個個人都互相關連<br />\n<br />\nQT 嚟計最鍾意 Bastards<br />\n納粹殺人係罪 但係美軍殺人就冇問題？<br />\n而且手段最兇殘嘅其實係所謂正義嘅Bastards<br />\n當你見到希特拉睇殺人電影睇到流晒口水 你會覺得佢係變態 其實你一樣睇噴血睇得好撚過癮<br />\n當Shosanna 同黑鬼炸戲院 你覺得呢班嗜血德國佬睇撚死 但其實你都係喺戲院睇緊殺人<br />\n唔知有冇過份解讀<br />\n<br />\nBtw Shosanna死嗰幕慢鏡+音樂好屈機<br />\nqt嘅神級暴力美學真係好頂癮"},{"pid":"5b99af3a9b17e90e342dc92303385a4932026334","tid":187021,"uid":103663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/heartinkstone/1402117393-2100735340_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fheartinkstone%2F1402117393-2100735340_n.jpg&h=d1557e63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd0c3259e7c7c4a93b0279e93469e61bc5f083d3","tid":187021,"uid":27562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"Les Mis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60abf7fcc1d0d64e7ab126da34bf65ebdc4265d8","tid":187021,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:21:51.000Z","msg":"Forrest Gump同the truman show"},{"pid":"cee9e0d62f0f4271f4340c19eaf7b7fa8042e36e","tid":187021,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"雷霆救兵<br />\n有陣時唔係下下有得揀<br />\n有得揀盡量揀返做自己、唔好迷失自我"},{"pid":"1810708fc41f3a04da31723a6c039ac82683c797","tid":187021,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"catch me if you can<br />\n<br />\n 細個睇完到而家都仲會間唔中學下佢咁扮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cdbbb06c85c21d1a6dd7012468c116d3a8406b","tid":187021,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"花樣年華<br />\n同春光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75de091fef0d3f77fbe6b3abe88fc722039ac37a","tid":187021,"uid":43610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:02:04.000Z","msg":"好似未有人講蝴蝶效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都曾經幻想過回到過去 改變做過既決定<br />\n但原來過去既每個決定影響千絲萬縷<br />\n根本無可能依我地喜好只去改變某一兩個決定 而唔造成蝴蝶效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以睇完好深刻 覺得宜家每個決定都好重要 唔可以再咁魯莽 同埋每刻都要做好自己 唔好令自己後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有 珍惜眼前人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二套係劉德華套大隻佬<br />\n[萬般帶不走，唯有業隨身]<br />\n睇完好撚心寒，開始愈黎愈相信因果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己種咗咩因，始終要自己受番<br />\n殺人要填命，永遠都無得走<br />\n害過人，要補償<br />\n籍此希望各香港人渣高官得到報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad002c55ca3a1d14037fb25052bb9a67c7f0848b","tid":187021,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>海神號遇險記<br />\n-人性，有無私、互助、鼓勵，有畏懼、羊群、退縮<br />\n-向命運低頭就輸<br />\n<br />\n魔法小奇兵<br />\n-有時要放低執著成見<br />\n-有時揸實一樣嘢可能比放開更傷<br />\n<br />\n怪形<br />\n-人互相猜疑比禽更恐怖更變幻無常<br />\n-講到尾：憑咩我要信你<br />\n<br />\n2001太空漫遊<br />\n-係進化定係被取代？係猿進做人定人取代猿，如果係後者HAL只係人類進化<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌得細力啲得唔得</span></blockquote><br />\n海神號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再見螢火蟲都係其實 睇完好深刻<br />\n覺得做人要識知足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b9e59e67b83cf9a378acaca50e205c77045a5b","tid":187021,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>海神號遇險記<br />\n-人性，有無私、互助、鼓勵，有畏懼、羊群、退縮<br />\n-向命運低頭就輸<br />\n<br />\n魔法小奇兵<br />\n-有時要放低執著成見<br />\n-有時揸實一樣嘢可能比放開更傷<br />\n<br />\n怪形<br />\n-人互相猜疑比禽更恐怖更變幻無常<br />\n-講到尾：憑咩我要信你<br />\n<br />\n2001太空漫遊<br />\n-係進化定係被取代？係猿進做人定人取代猿，如果係後者HAL只係人類進化<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">屌得細力啲得唔得</span></blockquote><br />\n海神號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再見螢火蟲都係其實 睇完好深刻<br />\n覺得做人要識知足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新嗰套海神號沉咗都唔抵可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcda02a052c3a616ca93eb9a232917493cb963ba","tid":187021,"uid":60136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"麥兜 菠蘿油王子"},{"pid":"6254f3c4968a5c22beab1e267c3b4b120e934448","tid":187021,"uid":78988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T14:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麥兜 菠蘿油王子</blockquote><br />\n喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be32cbe8d9caff91400dc673c35c