y":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T18:17:09.000Z","msg":"竟然冇人講chronicle"},{"pid":"3b002a55acd955554e1d2b98d79fe07797124e7a","tid":187021,"uid":104214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T21:03:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n套戲入面既主角周慕雲好似現實中好多人咁<br />\n就算遇過幾多條女都好，最愛既始終係&quot;蘇麗珍&quot;<br />\n即係每個人心目中都會有一個係&quot;最愛&quot;<br />\n可能唔係你宜家呢個，或者將來嗰個，而係一直留戀過去但已經返唔到轉頭嗰一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到1999，以下呢段影評補充：<br />\n顯然，周慕雲活在這種追憶的生活中，把過去當成永恆。在他和眾多女伴交往的過程中，蘇麗珍期時已幻化成虛擬的想像，白玲的旗袍和蘇麗珍的如出一徹，王靖雯寫武俠小說的筆觸和個性和蘇的極之相似，同名同姓的賭徒蘇麗珍全然是周慕雲思憶的投射。當他在的士上倚着白玲的肩，他的腦海其實仍然想着蘇麗珍，在窺看2046號房間像回看那段消失的時光。「離開2046，有的人相當容易，有的人卻花很長的時間」，他卻好像永遠被困在這列車裡。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好識睇"},{"pid":"4a7888f48679995e89d45961a1712803ac68e99d","tid":187021,"uid":36561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T21:21:24.000Z","msg":"13 Reason"},{"pid":"3c147f5cb9a44bff60dddedd29fa1971160d04a0","tid":187021,"uid":29719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T21:27:25.000Z","msg":"雲圖"},{"pid":"b1ef6eb7931da91709b473bcb4781aa68cc7eb27","tid":187021,"uid":17052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T22:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>the perks of being a wallflower<br />\n集結晒所有青春既問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We accept the love we think we deserve</span></blockquote><br />\n到而家都仲係我最鍾意既quote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3953107676e9fa878158008beb459f70b5aa6a","tid":187021,"uid":50613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T23:14:35.000Z","msg":"good will hunting<br />\n<br />\n唔好太過安於現狀 要敢想敢活 最緊要做番自己<br />\nrip robin williams<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8c6e2057c9d81bafacf59dfa5fe4fd72c06e37","tid":187021,"uid":56505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"喜馬拉啊星"},{"pid":"a0718e177ebe38a56c0345aa25556c857e579137","tid":187021,"uid":60588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>the perks of being a wallflower<br />\n集結晒所有青春既問題<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">We accept the love we think we deserve</span></blockquote><br />\n到而家都仲係我最鍾意既quote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢段真係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882818f41bb739d844a68a756d49334b02ee9fb7","tid":187021,"uid":16650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:03:14.000Z","msg":"the gift"},{"pid":"bc7f58bb19ce4541ca23f6ff7477a7f71d7f3247","tid":187021,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:19:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Watchmen<br />\n睇完會對社會人性好反感，所有嘢（姦殺兒童）都唔係上帝做成，係我地(人性)<br />\n反思咗人類存在其實唔重要，太渺小不值重視，我依家完全唔再關心所有嘢，例如環保／兒童被殺／貧窮，因為我地根本唔值得關心，人性本惡<br />\n另外乜嘢先係正義？殺幾百萬人換取幾十億人暫時嘅和平，定睇住核戰爆發一齊死？<br />\n<br />\nA live body and a dead body contain the same number of particles. Structurally, there's no discernible difference. Life and death are unquantifiable abstracts. Why should I be concerned?<br />\nOnce you realize what a joke everything is, being the Comedian is the only thing that makes sense. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係中二病發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果惡係人類造成, 咁唔通善就唔係? &quot;Apathy is the glove into which evil slips its hand&quot;, 你對世界唔關心正正係咪就係惡嘅表現, 殺幾百萬人、核戰...你覺得你幾時要面對呢個抉擇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本就庸人自擾"},{"pid":"2230439373a489429edea12dcf2f3e33d2d7f38b","tid":187021,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2046<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n套戲入面既主角周慕雲好似現實中好多人咁<br />\n就算遇過幾多條女都好，最愛既始終係&quot;蘇麗珍&quot;<br />\n即係每個人心目中都會有一個係&quot;最愛&quot;<br />\n可能唔係你宜家呢個，或者將來嗰個，而係一直留戀過去但已經返唔到轉頭嗰一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到1999，以下呢段影評補充：<br />\n顯然，周慕雲活在這種追憶的生活中，把過去當成永恆。在他和眾多女伴交往的過程中，蘇麗珍期時已幻化成虛擬的想像，白玲的旗袍和蘇麗珍的如出一徹，王靖雯寫武俠小說的筆觸和個性和蘇的極之相似，同名同姓的賭徒蘇麗珍全然是周慕雲思憶的投射。當他在的士上倚着白玲的肩，他的腦海其實仍然想着蘇麗珍，在窺看2046號房間像回看那段消失的時光。「離開2046，有的人相當容易，有的人卻花很長的時間」，他卻好像永遠被困在這列車裡。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好識睇</blockquote><br />\n都係要睇兩三次先感受到套戲既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06846395b105d97f1b8838c6f5b2a51e144484a5","tid":187021,"uid":56311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cloud atlas 雲圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次睇完都好攰但真係好正 會令你不停問自己生命嘅意義 同埋片尾曲好好聽<br />\n<br />\nOur lives are not our own. From womb to tomb, we are bound to others, past and present, and by each crime and every kindness, we birth our future.<br />\n<br />\nMy life amounts to no more than one drop in a limitless ocean. Yet what is any ocean, but a multitude of drops?</blockquote><br />\n同好，top 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人講係佛教輪回，反而我覺更似每一代人的革命一代影響一代"},{"pid":"2a0a0e1e971d507350c3194025beeae09b26294b","tid":187021,"uid":51593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T05:00:00.000Z","msg":"鐵達尼號 <br />\n肥温畫畫嗰幕 第一次見到除左阿媽之外 其他女人嘅lin 激發起當時仲係小朋友嘅我埋藏係心入面嘅性慾 之此之後就沉迷左睇av同打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20d304ecb2df27b722f467307d1a516ef071fb0","tid":187021,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐵達尼號 <br />\n肥温畫畫嗰幕 第一次見到除左阿媽之外 其他女人嘅lin 激發起當時仲係小朋友嘅我埋藏係心入面嘅性慾 之此之後就沉迷左睇av同打丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n影響好深遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就一世&hellip;"},{"pid":"4aa1f0852fe97bedf3658cd1cc4e9b18633483b9","tid":187021,"uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b4d90cded673937cdda8bf3669ada228d665e5","tid":187021,"uid":59869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"半支煙<br />\n成世人流流長, 點解唔搵d好野黎記住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑社會<br />\n人地選話事, 仲早過你地選特首<br />\n<br />\n黑社會2<br />\n&quot;由你來管理和聯勝, 香港會更加繁榮和安定&quot;<br />\n&quot;仆你個街!&quot;"},{"pid":"57f1302fdd7d702354d0f8fa1cb92031740b56b8","tid":187021,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:06:06.000Z"